---
title: Mexican Beef Loaded Wedges with Cheddar Cheese, Spring Onion and Lime
description: We love good Mexican Beef Loaded Wedges with Cream and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-beef-loaded-wedges-7675f297-7c6d8215.jpg
